@startuml
!theme plain
title 05. DPU Offload Boundary
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "Host services" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "DPU/SmartNIC" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "RDMA/NVMe-oF queues" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "Tenant isolation" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "Telemetry" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : I/O intent
N2 --> N3 : offload
N3 --> N4 : queue ownership
N4 --> N5 : policy enforcement

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
